title: Adult Cat Chicken Mousse
descriptions: With 80% Chicken and Grain Free, a complete food for adult cats.  All Natural adult wet cat food with 80% Chicken.  Naturo adult wet cat foods contain no artificial colours, flavours or preservatives and are free from grains which can often cause allergies.  Naturo Grain Free Cat Food contains added Taurine for normal heart function and vision and is supplemented with essential vitamins, minerals and oils for healthy skin and shiny coat.
